<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h3>
    <p>
      We are sorry to inform you that Personally Identifiable Information (PII) was detected in one of your files uploaded to ETDPlus.
      It is our policy to prevent public release of files that do not pass a PII check.
      The file in question was named <%= @file_name %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      For further information, please contact us through our contact form, at <%= root_url %>contact
    </p>
    <p> The specific contact information is listed as follows:
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Name</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.name') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Email</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.email') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Phone</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.phone') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Twitter</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.twitter') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Room Number</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.room_number') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Hours</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.hours') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Other Information</th>
            <td><%= t('pii_mail.other_info') %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </p>
    <p>The ETDPlus Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
